feed.title: KSC Wiki
feed.subtitle: Knights Satellite Club Wiki is your destination for all things CubeSat. We are a student organization from the University of Central Florida at the heart of the aerospace industry.

entry.title: Hello World!
entry.content:
This is the beginning of the KSC Wiki. We hope for this to be a hub where we can share our journey making CubeSats. Everything we do will be documented here making it easier for anyone to start thier very own mission.

Stay tuned for more!
